OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FEarly showery rain and
OL,6,Fthunderstorms clearing northeastwards
OL,7,Fto leave a largely dry day, with
OL,8,Fprolonged spells of hazy sunshine.
OL,9,FAnother exceptionally hot and humid
OL,10,Fday. Chance of thunderstorms arriving
OL,11,Ffrom the south during the evening.
OL,12,FFeeling humid.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTonight:FAn exceptionally hot end to
OL,15,Fthe day, with perhaps the chance of
OL,16,Ffurther heavy showers and
OL,17,Fthunderstorms moving northwards
OL,18,Fovernight. Another warm and humid
OL,19,Fnight.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
