OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FLargely dry with variable
OL,6,Fcloud and bright or sunny spells.
OL,7,FChance of heavy showers and
OL,8,Fthunderstorms arriving from the south
OL,9,Fduring the evening. Still feeling hot
OL,10,Fand humid.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FBands
OL,13,Fof showers, heavy and possibly
OL,14,Fthundery, moving east on Sunday,
OL,15,Fgradually introducing much fresher
OL,16,Fconditions. Largely dry with warm
OL,17,Fsunny spells on Monday. Scattered,
OL,18,Foccasionally heavy, showers Tuesday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
